            "content_1": "<p><strong>Base Unit</strong> — Mammoth AirStyler 5-in-1 with Coanda airflow<br><strong>Hair Dryer</strong> — High-speed drying attachment<br><strong>Left Curling Barrel</strong> — 32mm for left-side curls<br><strong>Right Curling Barrel</strong> — 32mm for right-side curls<br><strong>Volumizing Brush</strong> — Round brush for root lift<br><strong>Smoothing Brush</strong> — Paddle brush for sleek finishes<br><strong>Travel Pouch</strong> — Black protective case<br><strong>Heat Protectant Spray</strong> — 200ml bottle<br><strong>Silk Scrunchie</strong> — Premium hair accessory<br><strong>Digital E-Book</strong> — Hair care tips & styling guide</p>",
            "title_2": "Specifications",
            "content_2": "<p><strong>Weight:</strong> 400g<br><strong>Dimensions:</strong> 22 × 4.5 cm<br><strong>Technology:</strong> Coanda Effect + Negative Ions<br><strong>Cord:</strong> 1.9m with 360° swivel<br><strong>Coating:</strong> Ceramic<br><strong>Power:</strong> 1000W<br><strong>Temperature:</strong> 3 settings (60°C / 85°C / 110°C)<br><strong>Voltage:</strong> 110-120V / 60Hz<br><strong>Certification:</strong> UL 1727</p>",
